{"tid":2399040,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"拜登受訪稱習近平骨子裡沒民主 美中將激烈競爭","createTime":"2021-02-07T19:24:21.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-08T12:06:09.000Z","uid":337052,"like":12,"dislike":32,"uniUserReply":59,"replies":[{"pid":"23efa02160a6fecb8e62f995b09290db6a31bc26","tid":2399040,"uid":337052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T19:24:21.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"x-large\">拜登受訪稱習近平骨子裡沒民主 美中將激烈競爭</span></strong><br />\n最新更新：2021/02/08 02:28<br />\n<br />\n（中央社華盛頓7日綜合外電報導）<span class=\"red\">美國總統拜登接受媒體專訪指出，他預期美國與中國的關係將會是「激烈競爭」形式，而不是兩個世界強權之間發生衝突，拜登還提到中國國家主席習近平「骨子裡沒有民主」。</span><br />\n<br />\n美國哥倫比亞廣播公司新聞網（CBS News）今天播出拜登（Joe Biden）接受專訪的部分內容，拜登說從他就任美國總統以來，還沒有跟中國國家主席習近平談話。<br />\n<br />\nCBS主播問道：「美中關係可能是全世界最重要的議題之一。你為何還沒致電習近平？」<br />\n<br />\n拜登回答：「我們還沒有機會跟他通話，沒有理由不致電給他。別人告訴我，我跟習近平相處的時間，可能比任何世界領袖都還多，因為我擔任副總統時，曾與他有過24至25小時的私人會談，跟他旅行1萬7000英里。我很了解他。」<br />\n<br />\n拜登說：「他很強硬。但我沒有批評的意思，只是闡述現實，他骨子裡沒有一點民主。」<br />\n<br />\n「我一直以來都對他說，我們不必發生衝突。但是競爭將非常激烈。」<br />\n<br />\n他還提到：「我不會像前總統川普（Donald Trump ）那麼做。我們將專注於國際規則。」（譯者：陳彥鈞）1100208<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.cna.com.tw/news/aopl/202102080005.aspx\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cna.com.tw%2Fnews%2Faopl%2F202102080005.aspx&d=wuzGI5SyrIdJ%2FUQuqXTUigDrJ99PsHpDQ3gYSBhgLgU%3D&h=3d82f492\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.cna.com.tw/news/aopl/202102080005.aspx</a>"},{"pid":"3c8702e0ff46fd354d8af42ef6b90b7cb2a50ecf","tid":2399040,"uid":210140,"like":18,"dislike":1,"score":17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T19:26:00.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\"><strong><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">兩黨共識又輸</span></span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"e3ac4bdf35aa6bbadd2ee937a60de6c4dce4bf09","tid":2399040,"uid":255402,"like":5,"dislike":30,"score":-25,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T19:27:18.000Z","msg":"咁撚似侵初初上台講既野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a5e4186ea2776298296d7127280dc154c987e1a","tid":2399040,"uid":195995,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T19:29:41.000Z","msg":"佢諗住同習大大打君子波？"},{"pid":"81df053fd697dfcaf00a6ea234348af9e7bdc516","tid":2399040,"uid":17359,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T19:30:43.000Z","msg":"精神錯亂？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a1be7ad489d28961e94abbf0c623c37d3c34467","tid":2399040,"uid":103230,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T19:31:29.000Z","msg":"人地擺明帝制<br />\n九唔搭八<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83bf14561892c55f05b9a751432e9881245cda2c","tid":2399040,"uid":226955,"like":12,"dislike":2,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T19:34:40.000Z","msg":"共匪由day 1開始就已經冇民主啦，白登又暴露自己弱智"},{"pid":"c9e6eff73e5c1d58a8dcd8d15f33a8afd5b75b51","tid":2399040,"uid":89182,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T19:37:36.000Z","msg":"我們還沒有機會跟他通話<br />\n<br />\n嗱，呢啲咪叫識分尊卑<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/champagne.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aba1076e4c856daf3630ef939036e5d92f6affe7","tid":2399040,"uid":100986,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T19:38:07.000Z","msg":"白登: 要同中蟈公平競爭，最衰都係Trump"},{"pid":"63b7a1b74564833d6697b795a735c985fe346172","tid":2399040,"uid":337052,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T19:41:07.000Z","msg":"習近平骨子裡沒民主"},{"pid":"00a0fa9bb94224161cb75cc312d514e529102b9b","tid":2399040,"uid":48222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T19:42:57.000Z","msg":"CHINA JOE:阿媽係女人"},{"pid":"e438974e833e6fff6e9bbc6b16efd07dd16a0905","tid":2399040,"uid":251732,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"63b7a1b74564833d6697b795a735c985fe346172","tid":2399040,"uid":337052,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":5,"replyT